content: प्रोथ् {c1c} <ab>U.</ab> (प्रोथति-ते) {@--1@} To be equal to, be a match for, withstand (with <ab>dat.</ab>); पुप्रोथास्मै न कश्चत <ls>Bk. 14. 84</ls>; <ls n="Bk.">15. 40.</ls> {@--2@} To be able, adequate or competent. {@--3@} To be full or complete. {@--4@} To subdue, overpower. {@--5@} To destroy, slay.
